AnalysisName = "DS_OVEN_105" AnalysisComp = "DS (%)"
DS105 = select result.numeric_entry where sample_number = originalSample and analysis = AnalysisName and name = AnalysisComp order by sample_number
if (isNull(sampletype) or (sampletype = "DUP")) then if (isEmpty(DS105)) then RETURN endif else DS105 = 100 endif
AL_DS = (AL / DS105) * 100 Return AL_DS
